  "abstract": "P04t reproduces the raw-ROOT B-stack S00 count (640,737), the A-stack analysis gates, and the P04c event-matched row count (4,055) before fitting any model. Across A1-only, A3-only, and A1A3 topologies, the pooled winner is `cnn1d_waveform` with weighted res68 0.3562. The topology-specific lower bounds remain broad compared with duplicate-readout closure, so the result is a support-limited external-transfer bound rather than an adoptable energy/PID correction.",
